{"id":24647,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Katsuyuki Konishi (小西 克幸, Konishi Katsuyuki) is a Japanese voice actor and stage actor currently affiliated with Ken Production. He was the vice-chairman of the theater company Hero Q.\n\nShin Azuma and Hatsu Fujibaku are aliases of Katsuyuki Konishi for adult games and anime.","name":"Katsuyuki Konishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小西克幸（日语：小西 克幸／こにし かつゆき Konishi Katsuyuki，1973年4月21日[1]—）为日本第四代男性声优，胜田声优学院第11期生，贤Production所属，剧团HEROHERO-Q公司副座长。出身于和歌山县和歌山市。身高180cm，体重70kg，B型血，星座金牛座。家里分别有相差四岁的姐姐和弟弟。\n\n本身嗓音偏高，多有热血狂放的角色，同时其冷静低沉的帅气声线也是极大的特色，可以说是集冰火两种属性于一身的演员。","name":"小西克幸","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Katsuyuki Konishi est un seiyuu, il est affilié à Ken Production.","name":"Katsuyuki Konishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Katsuyuki Konishi (小西 克幸, Konishi Katsuyuki) es un actor de doblaje y actor de teatro japonés actualmente afiliado a Ken Production. Fue vicepresidente de la compañía de teatro Hero Q.\n\nShin Azuma y Hatsu Fujibaku son alias de Katsuyuki Konishi para anime y juegos para adultos.","name":"Katsuyuki Konishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"코니시 카츠유키","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"小西克幸","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小西克幸是日本的男性聲優。出身於和歌山縣和歌山市，所屬公司為賢Production。","name":"小西克幸","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Katsuyuki Koni